Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "type": "CRITERIA_POLYGONS",
    "inputPayload": {}
}

### Try to create job with invalid type
POST {{baseUrl}}/jobs
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "type": "INVALID_TYPE",
    "inputPayload": {}
}

